    <h3 class="heavy-font">Comprehensive STI Detection with Rapid, Accurate Results.</h3>
</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
The <span class="main-color heavy-font font-20"><b>sSPRT™ STI Panel</b></span> by FlashDx provides fast, multiplexed detection of the most common sexually transmitted infections (STIs) from a single swab sample. Powered by proprietary sSPRT™ technology, this panel identifies six key STI pathogens with high sensitivity and specificity, enabling clinicians to deliver prompt and targeted treatment. Its sealed cartridge design ensures safe and contamination-free testing, ideal for both clinical and point-of-care environments.
</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Compatible with the FlashDx-1000-E system, the STI Panel delivers results in under 60 minutes with only one minute of hands-on time. Internal process controls are built into each cartridge to ensure diagnostic integrity. This CE-IVDR certified panel is an essential tool for rapid STI screening and diagnosis, streamlining workflows in healthcare settings while maintaining diagnostic accuracy.
</p>

