Across our broad portfolio of microscope slides, laboratories recognize Trajan for quality, reliability and value in both slides and specialty glass.</p>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
When it comes to creating tissue slides, laboratory personnel find the perfect combination in our innovative and specialized slides with exceptional surface quality and optical clarity. The advanced surface coatings provide an optimal environment needed for tissue adhesion – and ultimately, successful diagnostic capability for a wide range of pathologies. Our dedication to quality and technology helps to provide reliable results within laboratories as they process and deliver multiple slides.</p>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
