Elevate your pathology lab solutions to new heights with cutting-edge digital technologies with unparalleled image quality. OptraSCAN’s OS-Ultra whole slide image scanner represent a revolutionary leap forward, empowering pathology labs with seamless, high-volume whole slide scanner pathology systems for comprehensive workflow and with enhanced imaging and Artificial Intelligence solutions. Our advanced Brightfield slide scanner pathology systems deliver exceptional whole slide imaging, ensuring precise and efficient slide images and analysis for enhanced diagnostic* accuracy.
