    <h3 class="heavy-font">Rapid, Reliable Detection of Group B Streptococcus (GBS).</h3>
</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
The <span class="main-color heavy-font font-20"><b>Group B Strep (GBS) Test</b></span> by FlashDx provides fast and accurate detection of Group B Streptococcus colonization in pregnant women. Utilizing sSPRT™ technology within a fully enclosed cartridge, the test identifies GBS from vaginal or rectal swabs with high sensitivity and specificity. Early detection of GBS is critical for preventing neonatal infections and guiding intrapartum antibiotic prophylaxis.
</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Compatible with the FlashDx-1000-E system, the GBS Test delivers results in under 60 minutes with minimal hands-on time. Its automated, sample-to-answer workflow ensures reliable performance with integrated process controls in every run. CE-IVDR certified, the GBS Test supports clinical decisions in obstetric care with speed, accuracy, and safety.
</p>

