<p class="heading-desc t-justify">The Xpert Carba-R QC Panel M219 is intended for in vitro use as a quality control to monitor the detection and differentiation of 5 beta-lactamase gene sequences (blaKPC, blaNDM, blaVIM, blaOXA-48, and blaIMP-1) when tested by the Cepheid Xpert Carba-R Assay on the GeneXpert instrument.

