														<label class="control-label"><i class="fa fa-align-justify label-icon"></i>Overview:</label>
														<p class="sub-heading">The Medimachine II is designed to provide both gentle tissue dissociation and fine homogenization using appropriate disposable devices with different technical features according to the required procedure.<br><br></p>
														<p class="sub-heading">The instrument has an interactive touch-screen for selection of operation mode and for consulting the on board manual. This specific screen has been selected for use wearing lab gloves. The software offers multi-lingual settings and two modes: manual and automatic.<br><br></p>

