                                                                                        The Medimachine II Dissociator is a benchtop instrument for the automated dissociation of tissues to obtain single-cell suspensions. Single-cell suspensions are a crucial prerequisite to achieve reliable results in cell separation, cell analysis, and cell culture. Moreover, the Medimachine II can be used for the homogenization of cells and tissues to extract biomolecules for molecular biology or protein biochemistry applications.<br>Medimachine II homogenizator provides high quality results for extraction of molecules for the analysis of chemical residues, virus, bacterias, etc.<br><br></p>

                                                                                        <p class="heading-desc t-justify">
                                                                                        Four types of disposables have been specially designed:<br>
