                                                                                        </tbody></table>

                                                                                        <p class="heading-desc t-justify">
                                                                                        A number of Medimachine II programs have been specifically developed to offer standardized procedures for the gentle dissociation or fine homogenization of various samples. Operator could add and remove new customized programs.</p>

