                        <div class="heading">

                                    <h3 class="heavy-font">
                                    e°CABIN™ is the world’s most advanced whole body Cryotherapy Cabin</h3>

                        </div>


                        <p class="heading-desc t-justify">
                        The <span style="color:#3D57A5"><b>e°CABIN™</b></span> is the world’s first most advanced electric and fully automated whole body cryotherapy cabin that has transformed the market with its patented, gas-free technology. Unlike traditional nitrogen-based cryotherapy chambers, the e°CABIN™ is electrically operated, making it safer, more cost-efficient, and environmentally friendly. Designed with user ease in mind, the e°CABIN™ requires no special infrastructure or professional installation, allowing seamless integration into any wellness or recovery facility.</p> 

                        <p class="heading-desc t-justify">
                        This revolutionary cabin uses six smart sensors to monitor skin temperature in real time, ensuring personalised and precise treatments for every client. Whether you’re looking to accelerate recovery, reduce stress, or enhance overall well-being, the e°CABIN™ delivers unmatched results in as little as three minutes.</p> 

                        <p class="heading-desc t-justify">
                        The e°CABIN™ redefines whole body cryotherapy with its fully electric, plug-and-play design and smart monitoring technology. Delivering precise, automated treatments, it ensures consistent results with effortless operation, making it the safest and most efficient solution for recovery and well-being.</p> 

