<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
The <b>Co‑Dx Logix Smart® SARS‑CoV‑2 Direct Saliva (DS)</b> assay is an <b>extraction-free, real-time RT-PCR test</b> designed to detect the RdRp and E genes of SARS‑CoV‑2 directly from minimally processed saliva, leveraging Co‑Dx’s patented <b>Co‑Primer™ technology</b>. This streamlined protocol—combining saliva with Proteinase K and brief heat treatment—eliminates the need for lengthy RNA extraction, allowing labs to increase throughput, reduce costs, and simplify workflows without compromising accuracy.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Clinically validated, CE‑IVD marked in June 2021, and compatible with a variety of qPCR platforms (e.g., Co‑Dx Box™, QuantStudio 5, CFX 96), the kit delivers reliable qualitative detection in approximately 90 minutes. It incorporates a human RNase P internal control to confirm sample quality and provides comprehensive specificity—demonstrated to have no cross-reactivity with common respiratory pathogens, while maintaining at least 96.7% positive agreement in clinical saliva testing.</p>




