<h3 class="heavy-font">
NGS-Powered Assurance for Food Safety and Environmental Monitoring.</h3>
  
</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Clear Safety™</b> is an automated next-generation sequencing (NGS) platform developed for food and environmental safety testing. Designed to meet ISO 17025 and AOAC standards, it enables high-throughput detection and characterization of pathogens like Salmonella, Listeria, and E. coli in complex matrices such as food, water, and agricultural products. By combining automated sample prep, sequencing, and advanced bioinformatics, Clear Safety™ delivers rapid, high-resolution insights including serotyping, virulence markers, and outbreak source tracing—empowering food safety professionals with accurate, scalable, and regulatory-compliant pathogen surveillance.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Purpose & Compliance</b><br>
Clear Safety™ Detection is tailored for food and environmental testing, delivering automated NGS-based pathogen detection and characterization in matrices like food, water, and agricultural products. The platform is validated for ISO 17025 and AOAC compliance—meeting industry standards for food safety labs.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Workflow & Analytics</b><br>
Optimized for high-volume sample processing, the system handles end-to-end prep of food/media samples, followed by sequencing to identify pathogens (e.g. Salmonella, Listeria, E. coli). Clear Labs’ analytics pipeline offers rapid pathogen ID, serotyping, virulence gene detection, and outbreak source tracking—highlighting its strength in supply chain monitoring.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Industry Benefits</b><br>
Food safety professionals benefit from faster turnaround times and genomic resolution that surpass traditional culture methods. Automation reduces labor costs and errors while offering a robust surveillance tool for compliance, risk mitigation, and tracking complex contamination events across supply chains.</p>


