<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<i>CONTROLS FOR INFECTIOUS DISEASE TESTING</i>
</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">INTROL TB Panel M114 is intended for use as a quality control to monitor analytical performance of M. tuberculosis (MTB) on the GeneXpert System. INTROL TB Panel M114 is formulated to monitor the detection of MTB and multi-drug resistant MTB (MDR-TB) mutations.

The World Health Organization (WHO) reports that one-third of the world’s population is infected with MTB. In 2009, 1.7 million people died from tuberculosis (TB) and 9.4 million new cases were reported. MDR-TB is increasing with some regions reporting as much as 28% of new TB cases are MDR-TB.

INTROL TB Panel M114 is provided for Research Use Only (RUO).
<p>



