                </div>','ChondroHEAL is a revolutionary concept in the field of regenerative medicine. The combination of an ultra-concentrated and ultra-filtered PRF, mixed with autologous thrombin, offers a new bioactive three-dimensional scaffold to use for cartilage defects and for tendon and ligament lesions. The benefits of having a slow release of growth factors over time (7 days) and the instant polymerization of the fibrin around the lesion, thanks to our delivery device, give surgeons a powerful tool for their practice..','https://biologicalinnovations.trade/chondroheal/','#','biologicalinnovations/Biological_Product_ChondroHEAL.png',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('10-JUL-25','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_ChondroHEAL',null,null,null,null,'Biological Innovations','DIS-0010','PRG-0049','PTY-0002',null,null,'SyS Laboratories','N',null,null);
