                                                    <p class="heading-desc t-justify">Disposable disaggregator with 35µm (orange) or 50µm (green) separator screens. H.D. Polyethylene casing. Sterile and non-sterile. The internal mechanical part is in stainless steel and is made up of a fixed screen with about 100 hexagonal bore-holes, around each of which there are 6 microblades. 1 ml liquid solution.</p><br>

