														<p class="sub-heading t-justify">SyntMate is a state-of-the-art instrument developed for regenerative surgery, providing precise control over tissue prepartion for Surgical applications. Its advanced process with its proprietery technology ensures consistent and high-quality results, crucial for the success of regenerative procedures. Designed for flexibility, SyntMate accommodates a wide range of tissue types, making it suitable for diverse surgical applications.<br><br></p>
