<b>Co‑Dx Logix Smart® ABC</b> is a <b>multiplex real-time RT‑PCR assay</b> developed with the patented <b>Co‑Primers™</b> technology, enabling rapid and accurate qualitative detection of Influenza A, Influenza B, and SARS‑CoV‑2 from upper/lower respiratory specimens and saliva. It integrates an internal positive control (RNase P) and comes complete with master mix, positive control, and negative control reagents, ensuring robust result integrity in clinical diagnostics.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Clinically validated under CE-IVD standards (Europe, Nov 2020), the kit offers high specificity and sensitivity—over 93% for Influenza A, and 100% for both Influenza B and SARS‑CoV‑2—tools tested across multiple qPCR thermocyclers, including Co‑Dx Box, Bio‑Rad CFX96, PCR Max ECO48, and more.</p>



