            </div>','iPRF contains IDRIA B 30ml tube and accessories for blood draw. IDRIA B offers to create injectable platelet-rich fibrin (iPRF), a fully autologous, blood-derived biomaterial having three-dimensional fibrin meshwork.  Like that of a PRF clot, while retaining the fluid nature, similar to platelet-rich plasma (PRP). Along with platelets and its growth factors, injectable PRF has predominantly mononuclear cells along with its growth factors and fibrinogen..','https://biologicalinnovations.trade/idria-b-iprf/','#','biologicalinnovations/Biological_Product_IdriaB.png',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('10-JUL-25','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_Idria B',null,null,null,null,'Biological Innovations','DIS-0010','PRG-0049','PTY-0002',null,null,'SyS Laboratories','N',null,null);
