    <h3 class="heavy-font">Multiplex Detection for COVID-19, Flu A/B, and RSV — Fast & Accurate.</h3>
</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
The <span class="main-color heavy-font font-20"><b>SARS-CoV-2/Flu A/Flu B/RSV Cartridge</b></span> by FlashDx delivers rapid, multiplexed detection of the most prevalent viral respiratory infections. This sSPRT™-powered cartridge enables simultaneous identification of SARS-CoV-2, Influenza A, Influenza B, and Respiratory Syncytial Virus (RSV) from a single patient sample, optimizing both clinical workflow and diagnostic confidence.
</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
With approximately 1 minute of hands-on time and a fully automated workflow on the FlashDx-1000-E system, results are delivered in less than an hour. The fully enclosed cartridge minimizes contamination risks, and internal process controls ensure high diagnostic integrity. Ideal for point-of-care and decentralized healthcare settings, this cartridge helps clinicians rapidly differentiate between common respiratory viruses with overlapping symptoms.
</p>

