<h3 class="heavy-font">
Safe Prefilled Formalin Container</h3>

</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<b>Achieve Safety when Handling Biopsy Containers</b>
</p>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
FormSAFE is an innovative prefilled container designed to prevent formalin exposure when working with biopsies. The formalin layer is protected by a specially designed floating shield fluid, engineered to be non-miscible with formalin, ensuring a constant barrier against toxic fumes.
</p>


<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
This protects operators at every step, from specimen collection in the operating room to the grossing step in anatomic pathology.
</p>

<div class="panel-body">
<table>
	<tbody>
	
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2" ><span class="main-color heavy-font font-15" ><b>SUPERIOR OPERATOR SAFETY</b></span></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="width-40 "><i class="fa-custom fa-layer-group"></i></td>
		<td><p class="heading-desc t-justify">
FormSAFE is a safer alternative to traditional pre lled containers. It <b>prevents operator exposure to formalin during collection, transportation and storage</b>. The  oating component above formalin phase doesn’t a ect the collected biospecimen and remains immiscible with formalin. Even when agitated, the  oating layer quickly reforms, always ensuring operator and specimen protection.</p></td>
	</tr>

	<tr>
		<td colspan="2" ><p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<span class="main-color heavy-font font-15" ><b>FLOATING SHIELD FLUID</b></span></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="width-40 "><i class="fa-custom fa-layer-group"></i></td>
		<td><p class="heading-desc t-justify">
to prevent the escape of fixative fumes</p></td>
	</tr>

	<tr>
		<td colspan="2" ><span class="main-color heavy-font font-15" ><b>10% BUFFERED FORMALIN</b></span></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="width-40 "><i class="fa-custom fa-layer-group"></i></td>
		<td><p class="heading-desc t-justify">
for specimen collection, transportation and storage</p></td>
	</tr>



	<tr>
		<td colspan="2" ><span class="main-color heavy-font font-15" ><b>EASY TO USE AND IMPLEMENT</b></span></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="width-40 "><i class="fa-custom fa-layer-group"></i></td>
		<td><p class="heading-desc t-justify">
FormSAFE  oating shield technology is easy to implement at the collection and grossing/processing stages because <b>it does not require any changes to laboratory work ow or protocols</b>. The endoscopist can easily remove the biopsy from the forceps by dipping them into the  uid without being exposed to formalin fumes or requiring formalin transfer. The histologist can open the container and pick up the specimen without being exposed to vapours.</p></td>
	</tr>

</tbody></table>
