<tr><td class="width-40 center-bullet "><i class="fa-custom fa-circle font-8 main-color"></i></td><td>Universal adaptability: It can be matched with common brands of pipettes (Eppendorf, Thermo Fisher, Rainin, etc.) in the market.</td></tr>
