<p class="heading-desc t-justify">VAHTS Target Capture Universal Blockers and Post-PCR Primer Mix for Illumina-TS contains Universal Blockers for IlluminA-TS Illumina-TS and Post-PCR Primer Mix for Illumina-TS two fractions. Among them, Universal Blockers for IlluminA-TS is a generic adapter blocking sequence directed at Illumina common DNA libraries. These universal Blockers are suitable for DNA libraries labeled with single or double ends of 6-8 bp Barcode. It can effectively reduce the series structure formed between different library molecules due to the annealing between joints during hybridization, as well as to reduce the non-specific hybridization and improve the medium target rate of hybridization capture reaction. Post-PCR Primer Mix for IlluminA-TS is a universal amplification primer directed to Illumina&#x27;s TruSeq DNA library. All components in the kit have gone through strict quality control and functional verification, which ensures the stability and repeatability of the experiment to a large extent.</p>

