rlying mucosa located primarily toward the basal layer of the tonsil.2The high sensitivity of anti-CD103 for hairy cell leukemia makes this marker valuable when distinguishing from other B-cell neoplasms.</div>          </td>        </tr>      </table>    </div>    <div class="antibody-link-button">      <a href="https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/3481/CD103_EP206" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','CD103 (EP206) on Hairy cell leukemia.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/3481/CD103_EP206','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_-437R-1-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-3481-cd103-ep206-91A6EAAB',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','Y',null,'CM/3481/CD103_EP206');
