<p class="heading-desc t-justify">AccurSTART One Step RT-qPCR Super PreMix (ONE TUBE) is a one-tube probe-based RT-qPCR master mix suitable for single or multiplex quantitative PCR detection using RNA as template (such as RNA virus). The enzyme in this master mix uses a hot-start technology based on enzyme modification, with a new generation of high-affinity Taq enzyme antibodies, to achieve efficient blocking and precise release.</p>
<br>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Combined with one-step reverse transcriptase and optimized chemical buffer, it supports pre-mixing of primers and probes in advance and the mix can be stored for a long time at low temperature. The sample to be tested can be added directly when using, no additional tube opening/pipetting operation. The anti-contamination system in this product can function at room temperature to eliminate the influence of other contamination on qPCR and ensure the accuracy of the results. This product is also compatible with fast programs, which greatly shortens the detection time.</p>

