c secretory epithelium, ejaculatory duct cells, epididymis, mammary epithelial cells, Merkel cells, and dermal fibroblasts.1A plethora of mesenchymal neoplasms have demonstrated PGP 9.5 expression.1,3,4</div>          </td>        </tr>      </table>    </div>    <div class="antibody-link-button">      <a href="https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/1993/PGP-9-5_Polyclonal" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','Auerbach plexus of nerve tissue is labelled by PGP 9.5 antibody on small bowel tissue.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/1993/PGP-9-5_Polyclonal','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_318A-1-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-1993-pgp-9-5-polyclonal-17B457DF',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','Y',null,'CM/1993/PGP-9-5_Polyclonal');
