llmarque.com/antibodies/CM/2005/Perforin_MRQ-23" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','Anti-perforin expresses punctate cytoplasmic staining in NK/regulatory T-cells of the spleen.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/2005/Perforin_MRQ-23','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_316M-1-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-2005-perforin-mrq-23-17A63F10',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','Y',null,'CM/2005/Perforin_MRQ-23');
