<p class="heading-desc t-justify">AccurSTART One Step RT-qPCR Probe Kit (Glycerol-free) is a glycerol-free reagent using RNA as a template (such as RNA virus), which is suitable for the development and design of lyophilized products. This product integrates the excellent performance of one-step dedicated reverse transcriptase and hot-start Champagne Taq DNA Polymerase with optimized buffer. Therefore, it has superior amplification efficiency, specificity and amplification balance for templates with different concentrations, and is compatible with different lyophilization processes.</p>

