rointestinal tract, particularly those of esophagus and stomach, as well as the pancreatobiliary tract including cholangiocarcinomas.1Other tumors expressing MUC5AC include carcinomas of the endometrium and lung.1MUC5AC may also be seen in Paget’s disease.3</div>          </td>        </tr>      </table>    </div>    <div class="antibody-link-button">      <a href="https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/2006/MUC5AC_MRQ-19" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','Gastric mucosa is labelled by MUC5AC antibody.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/2006/MUC5AC_MRQ-19','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_292M-9-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-2006-muc5ac-mrq-19-33DAD1A9',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','Y',null,'CM/2006/MUC5AC_MRQ-19');
