ll tumors, aberrant expression of MAGEC2 is exhibited in seminomas, but is absent in yolk sac tumor and embryonal carcinoma.5-7</div>          </td>        </tr>      </table>    </div>    <div class="antibody-link-button">      <a href="https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/3674/MAGEC2_EP405" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','MAGEC2 on seminoma.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/3674/MAGEC2_EP405','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_477R-1-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-3674-magec2-ep405-5CCF773C',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','Y',null,'CM/3674/MAGEC2_EP405');
