<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Vazyme pipette tip (racked) are disposable plastic consumables specially designed for daily pipetting operations. We offer three forms of packing, tips in box, tips with filter in box and tips in bulk. The boxed tips are ready to use after unpacking, which is convenient and fast, and can help experimenters improve experimental efficiency. The design with filter can effectively reduce aerosol contamination and protect precious and fragile samples. The tips in bulk are eco-friendly.</p>
<br>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Vazyme 10 μl/ 200 μl/ 1000 μl manual pipetting tips can be universally adapted to common pipettes on the market, including single-channel and multi-channel manual pipettes. The accurate scale mark facilitates confirmation of pipetting accuracy during use. The smooth inside of the tip can effectively reduce adsorption and reagent residues and improve pipetting accuracy. Strict production environment and quality control system ensure product stability, no source of DNA contamination, no DNase/RNase contamination, and no PCR inhibitor residue.</p>

