arque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','HMB-45 expression is found in the cytoplasm of the melanoma cells by anti-HMB-45.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/114/HMB-45_HMB-45','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_282M-9-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-114-hmb-45-hmb-45-AC9A3E15',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','Y',null,'CM/114/HMB-45_HMB-45');
