phocytes.1,2In conjunction with other markers, Ep-CAM can be used as an aid in determining epitheilial origin of neoplasms such as lung adenocarcinoma.2-4</div>          </td>        </tr>      </table>    </div>    <div class="antibody-link-button">      <a href="https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/1980/Ep-CAM-Epithelial-Specific-Antigen_Ber-EP4" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','Ep-CAM/Epithelial Specific Antigen (Ber-EP4) on colon.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/1980/Ep-CAM-Epithelial-Specific-Antigen_Ber-EP4','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_248M-9-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-1980-ep-cam-epithelial-specific-antig-10513B4D',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','Y',null,'CM/1980/Ep-CAM-Epithelial-Specific-Antigen_Ber-EP4');
