-Fibrillary-Acidic-Protein_EP672Y" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','GFAP antibody demonstrates a strong and diffuse, cytoplasmic staining reaction in astrocytes, oligodendrocytes, neurons and glia of the central nervous system.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/1963/Glial-Fibrillary-Acidic-Protein_EP672Y','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_258R-1-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-1963-glial-fibrillary-acidic-protein--E025D5B6',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','Y',null,'CM/1963/Glial-Fibrillary-Acidic-Protein_EP672Y');
